{"tid":1512983,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"快D登記做陪審員","createTime":"2019-08-28T06:27:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T07:45:30.000Z","uid":298130,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b80c7a89ea70b5cca88f12c7981ae9854428bab1","tid":1512983,"uid":298130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T06:27:09.000Z","msg":"📣📣📣📣📣<br />\n<br />\n‼‼‼‼‼<br />\n<br />\n原來班藍絲已經做緊，佢大規模咁登記成為陪審員，目的大家心知肚明，要幫手叫黃絲朋友報名‼‼‼<br />\n<br />\n申請程序好簡單，只需要<br />\n1.申請信<br />\n2.填好ROP-18 form:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.immd.gov.hk/pdforms/rop18.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.immd.gov.hk%2Fpdforms%2Frop18.pdf&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ2zUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=0d069ebf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.immd.gov.hk/pdforms/rop18.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n3.學歷證明<br />\n<br />\n就算你唔想做<br />\n都傳俾你身邊<br />\n*支持嚴正執法嘅朋友*<br />\n‼‼‼‼請即行動‼‼‼"},{"pid":"8a0128b780e963cd225a20bb1f35c4a215ddfbe5","tid":1512983,"uid":284522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T06:27:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/etSapPa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FetSapPa.gif&h=0cba6709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ2zUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=322ff218\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ2zUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=5b2fa7b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me